OL,3,CJudge riot warning as teens appear in
OL,4,Ccourt over Ballymena trouble
OL,6,FThree teenagers including a 15-year-
OL,7,Fold boy have been remanded into
OL,8,Fcustody charged with rioting in
OL,9,FBallymena on Tuesday.
OL,11,FThe judge described the rioting as
OL,12,F"despicable" and told the court it
OL,13,Fcaused "great trauma and fear".
OL,15,FThe court heard the youngest of the
OL,16,Faccused allegedly had a balaclava, a
OL,17,Frock and a bottle on his possession
OL,18,Fwhen he was arrested during the second
OL,19,Fnight of serious public disorder in
OL,20,Fthe Co Antrim town.
