OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy who was also charged
OL,7,Fafter being detained on Tuesday was
OL,8,Falso allegedly wearing a balaclava.
OL,10,FHis solicitor questioned the police
OL,11,Fofficer as to what his client was
OL,12,Factually doing when arrested, but the
OL,13,FJudge said there was sufficient
OL,14,Fevidence to connect the accused to the
OL,15,Fcharge of rioting.,
OL,17,FMichael Elliott, 18, of Lanntara,
OL,18,FBallymena is charged with rioting and
OL,19,Fwas also allegedly wearing gloves and
OL,20,Fa balaclava at the time of his arrest.
