OL,6,FHis solicitor told the court his
OL,7,Fclient accepts he was throwing stones.
OL,9,FAll three appeared separately at
OL,10,FBallymena Magistrates' Court on
OL,11,FThursday with police saying they could
OL,12,Fbe connected to the charges.
OL,14,FA police officer said he opposed bail
OL,15,Fover fears of more violence that could
OL,16,Flead to the "death or serious injury
OL,17,Fof namely foreign nationals living in
OL,18,Fthe area".
