OL,6,FHe also told the court a strong
OL,7,Fmessage needed to be sent out to
OL,8,Fothers thinking of taking part in
OL,9,Frioting.
OL,11,FThe judge agreed and remanded all
OL,12,Fthree into custody and warned that the
OL,13,Fviolence has caused "great fear and
OL,14,Ftrauma" not just in the local
OL,15,Fcommunity but in communities across
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland.
